==English==
===Etymology===
From {{F.}} ''[[fabuleux]]'' or {{L.}} ''[[fabulosus]]'', "celebrated in [[fable]]".

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

#[[Extraordinary]], especially in being very large.
#Very good; [[wonderful]].
#{{obsolete}} [[Mythical]] or [[legendary]]; [[incredible]].
#Of the nature of a [[fable]]; [[unhistorical]].

